15:38.959 --> 15:40.917
Time for flowers.
SAM: Or dinner.

15:40.959 --> 15:43.041
You guys know I'm married
to Charlotte? Charlotte King?

15:43.083 --> 15:44.834
JAKE:
You know, apologies
make sense to men.

15:44.875 --> 15:46.458
