I thought we were about?

18:36.083 --> 18:37.417
I don't know.

18:37.458 --> 18:39.667
I don't know how it affected
her brain chemistry.

18:39.709 --> 18:41.917
I don't know what was medication
and what was choice.

18:41.959 --> 18:43.083
But I think...

18:45.291 --> 18:49.125
What I'm trying to say
is that illness changes people,

18:49.166 --> 18:51.709
on the inside
and on the out.

18:51.750 --> 18:55.417
That's why the marriage vows say
"in sickness and in health."

18:56.959 --> 19:00.041
Now, I'm not saying
it's gonna be easy.

19:00.083 --> 19:04.333
