should hear Dr. Shepherd out.

19:06.542 --> 19:07.709
( knocking on door )

19:07.750 --> 19:09.041
Hi. Can I come in?

19:09.083 --> 19:12.458
Hi. Yeah, I was just about
to go buy some flowers.

19:12.500 --> 19:14.709
I'm not gonna be
any great shakes after surgery,

19:14.750 --> 19:18.041
so I wanna make sure that Nina
has something nice to look at.

19:18.083 --> 19:19.959
See you later.
Okay.

