organ rejection,

19:43.417 --> 19:45.041
and this is before
you get to implantation.

19:45.083 --> 19:47.041
I know the risks.

19:47.083 --> 19:49.041
Dr. Reilly laid them all
out for me twice.

19:50.542 --> 19:52.959
When I was younger,
my mom worried all the time.

19:53.000 --> 19:55.041
"Call me when you get there."
"Who are you going with?"

19:55.083 --> 19:56.166
"What time will you be home?"

19:56.208 --> 19:58.041
I just thought
that she was insane.

19:58.083 --> 20:00.125
And every time,
she said to me:

20:00.166 --> 20:04.375
"When you're a mother,
you'll understand."

20:04.417 --> 20:07.041
I wanna be so close to someone
