and protect and teach.

20:17.083 --> 20:19.041
So when I read about
Dr. Reilly's research--

20:19.083 --> 20:20.750
It's not a guarantee
that it will work.

20:20.792 --> 20:22.667
There are no guarantees
in life.

20:22.709 --> 20:24.041
But if something
is worth having,

20:24.083 --> 20:26.458
