21:24.959 --> 21:28.875
but Dr. Shepherd
is a very gifted neurosurgeon.

21:28.917 --> 21:33.041
This could be good, Laura.
It could get us back on track.

21:33.083 --> 21:36.500
Yeah, but it's all
really terrifying.

21:36.542 --> 21:38.667
More terrifying than life
without me?

21:38.709 --> 21:41.041
Look, I don't mean to--

21:41.083 --> 21:43.291
I'm scared too,
